---
title: Sea Bass in Creamy Cajun Sauce with Spiced Chips and Tomato Salad
description: Punchy and smoky with a spicy kick, Cajun spice mix contains ingredients such as chilli powder, ground cumin, oregano and thyme. The spiced Cajun sauce pairs perfectly with sea bass, a delicate white fish that's great for soaking up flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R06_W43_UK_L20072-4_Main_low_2-ec36d27e.jpg
